---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Chesham | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Chesham. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Chesham and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(13).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 30%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Chesham</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Chesham</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">HP5 · Plastering &amp; decorating across Chesham's Victorian terraces and 20th-century residential.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Chesham</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">A market town at the northern edge of the corridor — Victorian terraces in the town centre, suburban development rising up the Chess Valley sides.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Chesham is the furthest north-west point of the service corridor. The town has a mix of Victorian terraced housing in the older streets, 1930s–50s suburban on the valley slopes, and some modern development. Victorian solid brick terraces — no cavity — present the classic damp-driven plaster failure risk. The town sits on the River Chess, with some properties at floodplain level.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Chesham's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Damp on Victorian terraces</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The town-centre terraces are solid brick with no cavity — damp can track through and blow plaster from the inside face. It needs the cause treated, not just a re-skim.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Floodplain-level moisture</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The town sits on the River Chess, and some lower properties carry a higher damp exposure that shows up as plaster failure on ground-floor walls.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Settlement on the valley slopes</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The 1930s–50s suburban semis on the valley sides show the usual stepped and hairline cracking above openings, needing proper repair and re-skim.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">A Chilterns market town in the Chess valley.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Chesham is the furthest north-west point of the corridor. The town has Victorian terraced housing in the older streets, 1930s–50s suburban development climbing the valley slopes, and pockets of modern build. The River Chess runs through it, and the town centre retains a genuine market-town character.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">The solid-brick Victorian stock is the defining challenge here — and exactly the kind of damp-driven plaster work we handle properly.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Plaster repair and decorating.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Damp-related plaster repair on the terraces, crack repair and re-skims on the suburban semis, and interior and exterior painting throughout. We diagnose the cause of plaster failure before quoting — patching over damp just brings it back.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Honest assessment, fair fixed price agreed up front.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Chesham</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~30 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">At the top corner of the corridor, reached via the A404 and Amersham. Covered on planned Chiltern runs.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Damp-aware</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We diagnose the source of plaster failure on solid-wall terraces before specifying — the right fix, not just a cosmetic patch.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Access &amp; parking</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Terraced streets with permit zones we plan around; suburban slopes are straightforward.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Surfaces protected, site left tidy daily. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
  <div style="position:relative;height:clamp(300px,42vw,440px);">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(2).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
